trans-unit.source: Encapsulates the encryption algorithm used for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Innkapsler krypteringsalgoritmen som brukes for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The `<EncryptionMethod>` tag uses a Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) to identify the encryption algorithm that must be used to decrypt XML data.
trans-unit.target: Den `<EncryptionMethod>` koden bruker et URI Uniform Resource Identifier () til å identifisere krypteringsalgoritmen som må brukes til å kryptere XML.

trans-unit.source: The EncryptionMethod class encapsulates the `<EncryptionMethod>` tag defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EncryptionMethod innkapsler den `<EncryptionMethod>` koden som er definert av World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering spesifikasjonen finnes på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: Use the EncryptionMethod class to identify the encryption algorithm associated with the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> element or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: Bruk klassen EncryptionMethod til å identifisere krypteringsalgoritme som er knyttet til den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>element eller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>element.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: Use one of the URI identifiers defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en URI-identifikatorer som er definert i World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering-spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: All URI identifiers are accessible as static fields of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml> class.
trans-unit.target: Alle URI-IDer er tilgjengelige som statiske felt av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod> class without specifying the Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) of an encryption algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod>klasse uten å angi Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) for en krypteringsalgoritme.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> class specifying an algorithm Uniform Resource Identifier (URI).
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> klassen angivelse av en algoritme Uniform URI (Resource Identifier).

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod> class using the URI of an encryption algorithm.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod>klasse ved hjelp av URI for en krypteringsalgoritme.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod>

trans-unit.source: Use one of the URI identifiers defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en URI-identifikatorer som er definert i World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering-spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: All URI identifiers are accessible as static fields of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml> class.
trans-unit.target: Alle URI-IDer er tilgjengelige som statiske felt av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>

trans-unit.source: The Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes the algorithm represented by an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) som beskriver algoritmen representert av en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"></xref> object that encapsulates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"> </xref> objekt som innkapsler en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The GetXml method returns a representation of the `<EncryptionMethod>` element.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetXml returnerer en representasjon av den `<EncryptionMethod>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"></xref> object that encapsulates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Xml.XmlElement"> </xref> objekt som innkapsler en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptionMethod"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes the algorithm to use for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et URI Uniform Resource Identifier () som beskriver algoritmen som skal brukes for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The KeyAlgorithm property describes the Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) of the encryption algorithm used to encrypt data associated with either the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> element or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen KeyAlgorithm beskriver Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) for krypteringsalgoritmen som brukes til å kryptere data som er knyttet til enten den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>element eller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>element.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: Use one of the URI identifiers defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en URI-identifikatorer som er definert i World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering-spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: All URI identifiers are accessible as static fields of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml> class.
trans-unit.target: Alle URI-IDer er tilgjengelige som statiske felt av <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>klasse.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedXml>

trans-unit.source: A Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes the algorithm to use for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: En URI Uniform Resource Identifier () som beskriver algoritmen som skal brukes for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the algorithm key size used for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir algoritmen nøkkelstørrelsen som brukes for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The KeySize property describes the key size of the encryption algorithm used to encrypt data associated with either the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> element or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> element.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen KeySize beskriver nøkkelstørrelsen på krypteringsalgoritmen som brukes til å kryptere data som er knyttet til enten den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>element eller <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>element.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: The algorithm key size, in bits, used for XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Algoritmen nøkkelstørrelsen, i biter som brukes for XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: The KeySize property was set to a value that was less than 0.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen KeySize ble satt til en verdi som er mindre enn 0.
